    "monster4059": "<h1 class=monster>High Aspect of Orcus<br><span class=type>Huge elemental humanoid (demon)</span><br><span class=level>Level 29 Elite Brute<span class=xp> XP 30000</span></span> </h1> <p class=flavor><b>Initiative</b> +18        <b>Senses</b> Perception +23; Darkvision, low-light vision<br><b>Lesser Aura of Death</b> (Necrotic) aura 10; each enemy that enters or starts its turn in the aura takes 10 necrotic damage (20 necrotic damage while the high aspect of Orcus is bloodied).<br><b>HP</b> 664; <b>Bloodied</b> 332<br><b>AC</b> 41; <b>Fortitude</b> 43, <b>Reflex</b> 39, <b>Will</b> 40<br><b>Immune</b> disease, poison; <b>Resist</b> 20 necrotic, 10 fire, 10 force, 10 radiant<br><b>Saving Throws</b> +2<br><b>Speed</b> 6, fly 8 (clumsy)<br><b>Action Points</b> 1</p><p class='flavor alt'>(⚔) <b>Skull Mace</b> (standard, at-will) ✦ <b>Necrotic, Weapon</b></p><p class=flavorIndent>Reach 3; +32 vs AC; 3d8+10 damage, and the target is weakened (save ends). </p><p class='flavor alt'>⚔ <b>Double Attack</b> (standard, at-will) ✦ <b>Necrotic, Weapon</b></p><p class=flavorIndent>The high aspect of Orcus makes two skull mace attacks</p><p class='flavor alt'>⚔ <b>Tail Lash</b> (immediate reaction, when an enemy moves or shifts within 3 squares of the aspect of orcus, at-will) </p><p class=flavorIndent>Reach 3; +30 vs Reflex; 3d6+12 damage, and the target is knocked prone. </p><p class='flavor alt'><b>Alignment</b> Chaotic Evil       <b> Languages</b> Abyssal, Common<br><b>Skills</b> Arcana +26, History +26, Intimidate +27, Religion +26<br><b>Str</b> 30 (+24)      <b>Dex</b> 18 (+18)      <b>Wis</b> 19 (+18)<br><b>Con</b> 32 (+25)      <b>Int</b> 24 (+21)      <b>Cha</b> 27 (+22)</p><p class='flavor alt'><b>Equipment</b>: skull mace</p><br><p class=publishedIn>Published in E3 Prince of Undeath, page(s) 24.</p>",
